[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0116","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0116.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0046","title":"多款Unix系统 rlogin TERM环境变量缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"rlogin 程序在处理 TERM 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可向该环境变量传入超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 BSD/OS、DG/UX、Debian、Digital UNIX、FreeBSD、HP-UX、IBM AIX、NetBSD、NeXTstep、SGI IRIX、SunOS 等多种 Unix 操作系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0046"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.963","remediation":"针对各受影响系统版本，建议立即升级至修复版本（如 FreeBSD 2.2 及以上、HP-UX 11.00 及以上、IBM AIX 4.2 及以上）；如无法升级，可移除 rlogin 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/rlogin）或禁用 rlogin 服务（注释 inetd.conf 中 login 行并重启 inetd），改用 SSH 替代 rlogin 进行远程登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0046","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19203","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0046","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/brenonevs/prs-pentest/blob/001cf17eedeb4aad73618d3140ca1f5dc93e69b3/CVEs & POCs/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/622953dc0146a9a48737afdaeb97da06c1b9895d/1999/CVE-1999-0046.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0116.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0116.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0116.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0115","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0115.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0441","title":"Qbik WinGate 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Qbik WinGate 3.0、Pro 4.0.1 及 Standard 4.0.1 版本的 Winsock 重定向服务中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的网络数据包触发该漏洞，导致 WinGate 服务崩溃并引发拒绝服务。该漏洞利用了 Winsock Redirector Service 在处理输入数据时未正确验证缓冲区边界的问题，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程实施攻击，影响面涉及上述版本的 WinGate 代理服务器软件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0441"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.220","remediation":"升级 Qbik WinGate 至 4.0.2 及以上版本。如无法升级，在 WinGate 的 Winsock Redirector 服务配置中限制来源 IP 范围，仅允许可信内网地址连接。同时建议在边界防火墙上过滤对 2080/TCP 等 WinGate 默认端口的非授权访问，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD02221999.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/509","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19410"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0115.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0114","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0114.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0440","title":"Netscape Navigator Java 虚拟机字节码验证器远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Java Virtual Machine（JVM）字节码验证器组件存在安全缺陷，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页诱使用户访问，绕过字节码验证机制在目标系统上执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Netscape Communicator 和 Navigator 等浏览器产品所集成的 JVM 环境，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0440"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.073","remediation":"升级 Netscape Communicator 至 4.6 或更高版本（内置修补后的 JVM），或升级 Sun JDK 至 1.1.8/Java 2 SDK 1.2.2。临时缓解措施：在浏览器安全设置中禁用 Java Applet 支持，阻止恶意网页加载未校验的字节码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://java.sun.com/pr/1999/03/pr990329-01.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92333596624452&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1939"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0114.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0113","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0113.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0045","title":"Apache/NCSA/Netscape Web服务器 nph-test-cgi脚本任意文件列表漏洞","description":"Apache 1.1、NCSA HTTPd 1.5.2 及 Netscape Server 1.12/1.1/2.0 等早期 Web 服务器默认安装的 nph-test-cgi 脚本未对用户请求进行充分过滤，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向该脚本发送特制请求，遍历并列出服务器上的任意文件目录，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响多个主流 Web 服务器早期版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商建议移除 nph-test-cgi 脚本或升级至不受影响版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0045"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-12-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.793","remediation":"立即删除或禁用 nph-test-cgi 脚本（该脚本仅用于测试，不应部署在生产环境）；升级 Apache 至 2.4 及以上版本（1.3 系列已终止支持，1.1 含多个安全漏洞）；如使用 NCSA HTTPd，建议迁移至 Apache 2.4；Netscape Enterprise Server 用户应升级至 Oracle iPlanet Web Server 7.0+；同时在 Web 服务器配置中禁止 CGI 目录执行任意文件读取操作，严格控制 CGI 脚本文件权限为 750。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0045","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19536","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0045.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0045","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0045.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0045.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0045.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h7h3-hmx5-3w4r/GHSA-h7h3-hmx5-3w4r.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0045.yaml","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/9e4b769742ed57395763142c26029c2f9910f15b/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0045.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0113.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0113.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0113.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0112","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0112.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0439","title":"procmail 缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"procmail 邮件处理工具 3.12 之前版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于在处理 procmailrc 配置文件中的宏扩展时未正确校验边界，远程或本地攻击者可通过构造恶意的配置文件触发该漏洞，导致任意代码执行。此漏洞影响运行 openlinux 及其他使用受影响 procmail 版本的系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0439"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.947","remediation":"升级 procmail 至 3.12 或更高版本，该版本修复了配置文件扩展中的缓冲区溢出问题。对于老旧系统无法升级的，可在 procmailrc 中禁用危险宏扩展，并限制仅信任用户可修改配置文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0439"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0112.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0111","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0111.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0438","title":"Ramp Networks WebRamp 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"该漏洞存在于 Ramp Networks WebRamp 1.0 设备中，远程攻击者无需任何身份认证，仅需向目标设备的 UDP 5353 端口发送特制的恶意数据包，即可更改设备的网络 IP 地址，导致目标系统网络连接中断，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞攻击门槛低，影响 WebRamp 1.0 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等，建议用户尽快升级固件或限制 UDP 5353 端口的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0438"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.810","remediation":"升级到 Ramp Networks 官方发布的最新固件（1999 年已提供补丁），在网络边界防火墙阻断发往 UDP 5353 端口的入站流量，并限制对 WebRamp 设备的远程管理访问来源 IP，防止未授权配置篡改。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0438"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0111.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0110","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0110.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0044","title":"SGI IRIX fsdump 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.2 操作系统中 fsdump 命令存在本地权限提升漏洞。由于 fsdump 在处理敏感文件时未能正确限制普通用户的访问权限，本地攻击者可通过修改系统敏感文件将自身权限提升为 root 超级用户，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.2 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0044"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-12-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.660","remediation":"升级至 SGI IRIX 6.3 及以上版本以修复 fsdump 权限提升漏洞。临时缓解措施：执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/fsdump` 移除 fsdump 的 setuid 位，阻止非授权用户以 root 权限运行；同时通过 `chmod 700 /usr/sbin/fsdump` 限制仅 root 用户可执行，防止本地用户提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19280","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0044.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0044","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0044.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0044.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0044.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0044.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d1211931-bc17-4b72-a817-dc1a2d02bd86.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0110.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0109","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0109.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0437","title":"Ramp Networks WebRamp Router HTTP Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"WebRamp 路由器 HTTP 服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标设备的 HTTP 端口（默认 80）发送特制的恶意字符串，导致 HTTP 服务进程崩溃，造成设备无法正常提供 Web 管理功能。该漏洞影响 Ramp Networks WebRamp 系列路由器，攻击者无需认证即可触发，但需能访问目标设备的 HTTP 服务端口。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0437"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.680","remediation":"建议将 WebRamp 路由器固件升级至厂商最后发布的版本。在防火墙层面限制仅允许可信 IP 访问路由器的 HTTP 管理端口（80/443），避免暴露在公网。如无需远程管理，建议禁用 HTTP 管理界面。此产品已停止支持，长期建议更换为仍在安全更新期内的现代路由器设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0437"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0109.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0108","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0108.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0436","title":"HP HP-UX Domain Enterprise Server Management System 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 Domain Enterprise Server Management System (DESMS) 存在权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者利用 DESMS 组件在权限管理上的缺陷，可将其权限提升至 root 级别，进而完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 多个版本，需本地系统访问权限方可利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议用户应用 HP 官方安全补丁以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0436"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.550","remediation":"安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9903-095 对应的 DESMS 补丁包（如 PHSS_* 系列补丁）。如无需 DESMS 功能，可移除或停止相关服务（/sbin/init.d/desms stop；rm /sbin/init.d/desms）。限制本地控制台访问权限，仅允许受信管理员登录。建议升级至受支持的 HP-UX 版本（11i v3 以上），其默认不包含 DESMS 组件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9903-095"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0108.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0107","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0107.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0435","title":"HP HP-UX MC/ServiceGuard 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统的 MC/ServiceGuard 与 MC/LockManager 组件存在权限管理缺陷，本地用户通过 SAM 工具可利用该漏洞获取系统高级权限，实现权限提升。攻击者需具有目标系统的本地账号才能发起攻击，成功利用后可完全控制受影响的 HP-UX 系统，导致机密性、完整性和可用性丧失。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0435"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.417","remediation":"建议立即安装 HP 针对 MC/ServiceGuard 和 MC/LockManager 发布的安全补丁（HP-UX 11.00 及更早版本对应的 PHSS 补丁包），将 MC/ServiceGuard 和 MC/LockManager 升级至修复后的版本。如无法立即打补丁，可在 /etc/PATH 中限制普通用户对 SAM 命令的访问权限，移除 /usr/sbin/sam 等二进制文件的 setuid 位，并通过 SAM 授权配置文件限制仅允许受信任管理员用户使用该工具。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0435"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0107.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0106","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0106.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0434","title":"XFree86 xfs 本地符号链接攻击权限提升漏洞","description":"XFree86 xfs 字体服务器组件在处理文件操作时存在符号链接（symlink）攻击漏洞。由于 xfs 未能充分验证文件路径中的符号链接指向，本地攻击者可通过精心构造的符号链接将文件写入本无权访问的受限目录，进而实现权限提升或触发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 NetBSD 等 Unix 衍生操作系统，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，利用方式简单，危害等级高危（CVSS 7.5）。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0434"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.283","remediation":"升级 XFree86 至已修复 symlink 漏洞的版本（NetBSD 建议跟进 1999 年 3 月后的补丁），并将 xfs 字体服务以非特权用户身份运行于 chroot 隔离目录。临时缓解措施：在 /etc/rc.conf 中关闭 xfs 服务或在内核层为受限目录设置不可变标志（chflags schg），避免本地用户通过符号链接创建文件导致权限提升或拒绝服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/359"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0106.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0105","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0105.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0042","title":"华盛顿大学 IMAP 与 POP 服务器缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"华盛顿大学实现的 IMAP 和 POP 服务器中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向运行 imapd 服务的 Linux 系统发送特制请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，进而造成远程代码执行或任意文件读取。该漏洞影响使用华盛顿大学实现 IMAP/POP 协议套件的 Linux 系统，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0042"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.303","remediation":"升级 UW IMAP 至 4.5 及以上版本，该版本修复了 imapd 及 popd 中的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，建议禁用 IMAP/POP 服务，改用 SSH 隧道加密访问邮件，或在防火墙层面限制对 143/110 端口的访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0042","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/340","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0042","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0042.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/imap.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/imap_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83099/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-00xx/CVE-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0105.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0104","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0104.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0041","title":"多款Unix系统libc NLS组件缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NLS（自然语言服务）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向受影响系统发送特制的 NLS 请求触发缓冲区溢出，导致系统崩溃或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 UNICOS 9、MAX 1.3、AIX 4.2、IRIX 6、RedHat 4、Slackware 3、libc 5.2.18 及 mk 1.5 等多个 Unix 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。由于涉及系统核心库组件，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0041"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.153","remediation":"对于 Red Hat Linux 4/Slackware 3 等 Linux 系统，应升级至现代发行版并确保 glibc 版本高于 2.0（含 NLS 缓冲区溢出修复）；IBM AIX 4.2 用户请安装 APAR IX70456 补丁或升级至 AIX 5.3 及以上版本；SGI IRIX 6 用户应安装补丁 3369 或升级至 IRIX 6.5.4+。如无法升级，可移除 nls 可执行文件的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/nls），并限制仅受信用户可执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0041","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19551","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0041","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f47735aa52980ccd9473eed79b62a27c199a2cfa/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0041.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pqw7-9pjx-g2x6/GHSA-pqw7-9pjx-g2x6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/SSVC/data/1999/CVE-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0104.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0103","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0103.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0038","title":"BSD xlock 缓冲区溢出本地代码执行漏洞","description":"BSD 操作系统中 xlock 屏幕锁定程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 xlock 程序发送特制的超长输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存中的执行流程，实现以 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响多个 BSD 衍生系统，攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限，无需认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 8.4，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0038"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.473","remediation":"升级 xlock 至 xlockmore 2.5 及以上版本，或从操作系统厂商获取对应补丁（Sun 补丁 ID 10145）。在无法升级的环境中，限制不可信用户本地登录权限，移除 xlock 的 setuid root 权限位以阻止提权，或使用其他屏幕锁定工具替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0038"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0103.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0101","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0101.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0037","title":"FreeBSD Metamail 任意命令执行漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统自带的 metamail 邮件处理工具存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制的 MIME 邮件消息，在消息头中嵌入恶意命令。当用户使用 metamail 处理该恶意邮件时，漏洞被触发，导致以当前用户权限在系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，但需要用户主动触发邮件处理操作，影响范围较广。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0037"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-05-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.340","remediation":"升级 metamail 至已过滤 MIME 邮件头 shell 元字符的修补版本；若无法升级，建议直接卸载 metamail（pkg delete metamail）并改用 procmail 或 maildrop 等现代邮件处理工具替代；同时配置邮件客户端不自动调用 metamail 处理来自不可信来源的 MIME 邮件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0037"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0101.toml"}]